These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, metal, indie
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of metal##1
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | house | disco | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, snake, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | rabbit | snake | ferret | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, camping, woodworking, photography
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | woodworking | singing | camping | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, train, motorbike
1. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | train | airplane | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
